** How to build the web interface directly from the Git source:

1. Install Node.js and npm (provided by your Linux distribution)

2. Install gulp and bower

      npm install gulp bower

3. Install all the remaining node modules

      npm install

4. Download and install the bower components

      cd client/
      ../node_modules/.bin/bower install

5. Build the frontend files

      cd ..
      ./node_modules/.bin/gulp


** How to load the express server

Simply type in the directory html the following command:

     npm run start

